{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the Swin Transformer is selected for feature extraction.",
    "Swin Transformer adopts a hierarchical structure, creating layered representations by initially using small-sized patches and gradually merging adjacent patches into deeper layers of the Transformer.",
    "When IoU = 0.5:0.05:0.95, mAP is 0.674.",
    "When IoU = 0.5, mAP 50 is 0.862.",
    "When IoU = 0.75, mAP 75 is 0.793."
  ]
}